          <div class="instructions">
            <ul>
              
              <li>Instructors can create templates in template section in the nav bar</li>
              <li>Direct into template section</li>
              <li>SCreate the template in the upper right corner</li>
              <li>Enter the name in Template name input box and click create</li>
              <li>You can see the DIY template page based on the template we provide</li>
              <li>If you want to add more information, click the bottom left plus sign in the first red box</li>
              <li>If you don’t want any part of the template, you can click the trash bin sign on the right side
              </li>
              <li>If you want apply any custom template, click the choose file button at the bottom and upload the template you want to use</li>
              <li>After you submit the template, it will shows  on the main page of template</li>
            </ul>
