              <li>You must have at least one template before you are able to create recommendation</li>
              <li>Click the create recommendation button on the top right to create send the recommendation template to students to ask students fill the recommendation questionnaire
              </li>
              <li>The sending email window will pop up. Instructors should choose a template, and then fill in the student’s email address, the subject of the email and the content.
              </li>
              <li>Instructors can check whether the student has filled the form by the form status on the Recommendations page. A green check mark means the form is completed.
              </li>
              <li>After the form is filled, instructors can preview the recommendation letter, edit or save the letter, and then download the letter as a doc file.
              </li>
              
            </ul>
          </div>
